Bedroom was absolute luxury and after the ordeal when we arrived, we felt like staying in the hotel room all night but decided to venture out regardless.	Stayed here for 5 nights and the room is great with two twin beds and two bathrooms, truly a luxury for how much we pay for.	The hotel is located in an upscale neighborhood and within a very short walk of the nearest metro station.	The location didn’t seem that great in the beginning, but we realized that by taking the bus instead of the subway (2 bus lines are just 2 minutes away and those buses covered all our needs) it was easy and cheap to get around.